A Question of Death (2008). [5 hrs 40 mins]
A collection of Phryne Fisher short stories

If you think you would like entertaining audio books about a glamorous young lady private investigator in Melbourne in the late 1920's, then you will like Ms Phryne Fisher.
Is the heroine rather too perfect, lucky, beautiful and talented - yes of course she is! But, this series is a lot of escapist fun. Be warned that there are even some sex scenes - though tastefully done of course!
(Those familiar with Melbourne, Australia will recognize many landmarks and places still in existence today).


Enjoy and Seed!!
